scenes.description: Nerissa Ravencroft talks about her first EP 'In My Feelings' and introduces the encore song.
Nerissa Ravencroft performs her original song 'Sweetest Scarlet'.
Closing MC section where Nerissa thanks her fans (Jailbirds) and a final message appears on screen.
